I've never cooked a dish twice.

00:35:00.610 --> 00:35:01.690
APRAJITA JAIN: Wow.

00:35:01.690 --> 00:35:02.606
SANJEEV KAPOOR: Never.

00:35:02.606 --> 00:35:04.900
APRAJITA JAIN: Of all these
shows, it never happened?

00:35:04.900 --> 00:35:06.524
SANJEEV KAPOOR: No,
because the reason,

00:35:06.524 --> 00:35:11.440
I'll tell you, because
when we cook on TV,

00:35:11.440 --> 00:35:13.810
I do very simple dishes.

00:35:13.810 --> 00:35:16.850
I don't do something
which is complicated.

00:35:16.850 --> 00:35:21.760
So because it's very simple,
and I normally don't even plan.

00:35:21.760 --> 00:35:26.020
I just do whatever
comes to my mind.

00:35:26.020 --> 00:35:30.910
We have lots of ingredients
